::Prowl::

Prowl raises an eyesbrow as Iron Raptor stays in robot mode. He shruggs. It 
was her skin, not his ... but he didn't want her getting more hurt.

He looks at her, a strange expression in his eyes. "Please. It will be easier 
on bot of us.." That was a lie to an extent, Prowl realizes as he says it, 
Iron Raptor would be easier to carry in her robot mode, but if she was 
repaired, it was fine with him.
